19:43.969 --> 19:44.904
[screams]

19:56.448 --> 19:58.448
We gotta run now!

19:58.450 --> 20:00.218
Go!

20:00.220 --> 20:03.888
Welcome to Blood
Fest, mother fuckers!

20:03.890 --> 20:04.655
Guys!

20:04.657 --> 20:05.925
