20:24.213 --> 20:25.813
These have chainsaws!

20:32.188 --> 20:33.187
Hey!

20:33.189 --> 20:34.489
Come and get it!

20:36.926 --> 20:38.125
No.

20:38.127 --> 20:39.260
No, no, no, no, no,
no, no, no, no, no, no!

20:39.262 --> 20:40.161
No!
No!

20:40.163 --> 20:41.031
No!

20:46.669 --> 20:50.005
And remember, there's
no horror without hope!

20:50.007 --> 20:54.776
If you know the rules,
you just might make it!

20:54.778 --> 20:57.781
The rest of you are dead!

21:05.824 --> 21:07.024
Everyone's going
to the main gate.

21:07.026 --> 21:08.526
It's going to be a death trap.
This way!

21:13.900 --> 21:15.101
[screams]

21:20.140 --> 21:21.639
