21:21.641 --> 21:22.840
SAM: Found a light.

21:22.842 --> 21:23.407
Oh!

21:23.409 --> 21:24.677
Oh my God!

21:31.986 --> 21:33.219
Did you hear something?

21:33.221 --> 21:34.452
Yeah.

21:34.454 --> 21:35.288
Besides chainsaws,
death screams, and me

21:35.290 --> 21:36.991
