21:39.726 --> 21:41.261
No, there's something.

21:41.263 --> 21:42.762
It's over there.

21:42.764 --> 21:45.833
[suspenseful music]

21:51.106 --> 21:53.107
Wh... wh... wh... wh... wha...
wha... what are you doing?

21:53.109 --> 21:54.175
You can't open that door!

21:54.177 --> 21:55.442
It'll be like a
cat or like a rake.

21:55.444 --> 21:56.910
And then we'll all
breathe a sigh of relief.

21:56.912 --> 21:59.414
And then something will pounce
from the other direction!

21:59.416 --> 22:01.249
James Wan has made a
career on that shit, Dax!

22:01.251 --> 22:02.216
Please don't!

22:02.218 --> 22:03.117
Shut up, Krill!

22:03.119 --> 22:03.850
Please!

22:03.852 --> 22:06.923
[suspenseful music]

22:18.936 --> 22:19.635
KRILL: See?

22:19.637 --> 22:22.871
I fucking said so!

22:22.873 --> 22:23.741
Ashley!

22:31.317 --> 22:32.682
No signal.

22:32.684 --> 22:33.850
How fucking cliche is that?

22:33.852 --> 22:34.784
Oh, my God.
Oh, my God!

22:34.786 --> 22:35.719
Oh, my God!
Oh, my God!

22:35.721 --> 22:36.320
Oh, my God!
Oh, my God!

22:36.322 --> 22:36.920
Oh, my God!

22:36.922 --> 22:37.654
Oh, my God!

