ASHLEY: These rules
are ridiculous.

27:05.947 --> 27:08.448
Ashley, Ashley,
Ashley, Ashley.

27:08.450 --> 27:09.351
Let me see that badge.

27:12.920 --> 27:15.522
Yeah, I think I
should hold on this.

27:15.524 --> 27:16.591
Why?

27:16.593 --> 27:17.458
Because I don't
trust the monster squad

27:17.460 --> 27:19.092
to get us out of here alive.

27:19.094 --> 27:20.361
Are we going backwards?

27:20.363 --> 27:21.329
It's upside down.

27:21.331 --> 27:22.430
Do you trust me?

27:22.432 --> 27:26.066
Babe, no.

27:26.068 --> 27:27.602
You're an actress.

27:27.604 --> 27:28.803
All right, let's keep moving.

27:28.805 --> 27:30.539
Well, uh, wh... wh... whoa!
Wait a minute.

27:30.541 --> 27:32.006
Wait a minute.

27:32.008 --> 27:33.975
Maybe we should double-back
and find a different route.

27:33.977 --> 27:34.942
Double-back?

27:34.944 --> 27:37.379
This is a straight shot.

27:37.381 --> 27:38.846
Oh, wait.

27:38.848 --> 27:41.685
You don't think we're going
to wake the dead, you know?

27:41.687 --> 27:43.386
Like get attacked by zombies?

27:43.388 --> 27:44.354
Maybe.

27:44.356 --> 27:46.055
Are you serious?

27:46.057 --> 27:46.922
You're right.

27:46.924 --> 27:48.157
We should be really respectful.

27:48.159 --> 27:50.959
Excuse me, sir or madam,
I'm so sorry to tread

27:50.961 --> 27:52.630
on your forever resting place.

27:52.632 --> 27:53.499
[evil chuckle]

27:56.402 --> 27:58.001
Those are props.

27:58.003 --> 28:01.037
This is not a real
graveyard, OK?

28:01.039 --> 28:02.707
Do you honestly think
that Walsh wouldn't spring

28:02.709 --> 28:04.676
for real tombstones
but went ahead

28:04.678 --> 28:07.178
and got a boatload
of corpses from...

28:07.180 --> 28:09.013
God knows where you get corpses!

28:09.015 --> 28:11.115
And then he figured out
a way to animate them.

28:11.117 --> 28:13.585
And then he buried
them here in the hopes

28:13.587 --> 28:16.120
that we would come
tromping through

28:16.122 --> 28:19.091
and make a little too
much noise, wake the dead,

28:19.093 --> 28:20.660
and get attacked by zombies.

28:20.662 --> 28:23.063
Well, there's no such
thing as zombies!

28:27.402 --> 28:28.502
What?

28:28.504 --> 28:31.538
It's just... that's
usually when...

28:31.540 --> 28:33.674
when something happens to you.

28:33.676 --> 28:36.477
Like what?

28:36.479 --> 28:37.444
Ah!

28:37.446 --> 28:38.313
That.

28:41.283 --> 28:43.016
Lenjamin!

28:43.018 --> 28:46.222
[screams]

28:49.559 --> 28:51.626
Maybe he's OK.

28:51.628 --> 28:53.061
[belch]
ASHLEY: Oh!

28:53.063 --> 28:54.062
Maybe not!

28:54.064 --> 28:57.134
[music playing]

29:03.474 --> 29:04.441
The cabin!

29:04.443 --> 29:05.442
The cabin!

29:05.444 --> 29:06.310
Go!

