DAX: Go!

29:17.457 --> 29:18.355
SAM: This way!

29:18.357 --> 29:19.222
Oh, my God!

29:19.224 --> 29:19.956
It smells like dead people!

29:19.958 --> 29:20.792
Smells like dead people!

29:20.794 --> 29:21.793
DAX: Come on!
Quickly!

29:21.795 --> 29:23.795
Get the door!
Get the door!

29:23.797 --> 29:24.462
KRILL: Go!
Get the doorbell!

29:24.464 --> 29:26.163
Hello!
Help us!

29:26.165 --> 29:27.130
HINCKLEY: I'm sorry!

29:27.132 --> 29:28.299
We're all full!

29:28.301 --> 29:30.436
I'm sorry there's no
more room in here!

29:30.438 --> 29:31.202
What?

29:31.204 --> 29:32.270
HINCKLEY: We have a...

29:32.272 --> 29:33.472
we have a pregnant
woman in here.

29:33.474 --> 29:36.274
And, uh, we have...
actually, we have two

29:36.276 --> 29:38.477
pregnant women in here and...

29:38.479 --> 29:40.847
DAX: Hinckley.

29:40.849 --> 29:44.283
Barricade the door.

29:44.285 --> 29:45.184
I was...

29:45.186 --> 29:47.085
I was trying to open the lock.

29:47.087 --> 29:48.521
The lock was kind of tricky.

29:48.523 --> 29:49.390
He's gone.

29:51.726 --> 29:52.893
He's gone.

29:52.895 --> 29:55.094
And he was going to
direct a rom-com.

29:55.096 --> 29:57.430
I was going to be the rom!

29:57.432 --> 29:58.364
Dax!

29:58.366 --> 29:59.299
What do we do?

29:59.301 --> 30:01.234
How should I know?
Huh?

30:01.236 --> 30:02.703
We're probably all dead.

30:02.705 --> 30:04.473
And not just die in our sleep
dead, which is bad enough,

30:04.475 --> 30:06.273
but "being eaten
alive by zombies,"

30:06.275 --> 30:09.243
screaming, "waiting for
it all to end" dead.

30:09.245 --> 30:11.646
SAM: Hey, can I have a minute?

30:11.648 --> 30:12.581
KRILL: You'll be OK.

30:12.583 --> 30:13.414
Don't cry.

30:13.416 --> 30:16.217
SAM: That is not helping.

30:16.219 --> 30:18.353
OK, we need to come
up with a plan.

30:18.355 --> 30:19.454
I don't know what to do.

30:19.456 --> 30:20.590
I don't know shit!

30:20.592 --> 30:21.389
Dax!

30:21.391 --> 30:22.725
All you know is shit!

30:22.727 --> 30:25.528
But that shit is of
particular value right now!

30:25.530 --> 30:27.663
We've got a dozen
horror movies between us

30:27.665 --> 30:29.800
and actually
surviving this mess.

30:29.802 --> 30:32.536
Walsh is using every
trope in the book.

30:32.538 --> 30:34.872
Jesus, if I was a
virgin, I'd probably

30:34.874 --> 30:38.241
have a fighting chance.

30:38.243 --> 30:39.743
You're not a virgin?

30:39.745 --> 30:43.848
The point is that no one knows
these movies better than you.

30:43.850 --> 30:46.416
So we need you to
pull it together

30:46.418 --> 30:49.721
and help us get out of here.

30:49.723 --> 30:51.556
OK, OK.

30:51.558 --> 30:52.490
All right.

30:52.492 --> 30:53.626
Let's think here.

30:53.628 --> 30:56.862
OK, so what are we
dealing with here?

30:56.864 --> 30:57.930
Huh?

30:57.932 --> 30:59.765
Nothing outside
was running, right?

30:59.767 --> 31:00.533
No Snyders?

31:00.535 --> 31:02.668
No Boyles?
OK.

31:02.670 --> 31:03.769
We know how to kill them.

31:03.771 --> 31:05.204
HINCKLEY: How?

31:05.206 --> 31:07.172
KRILL: Oh, shit.

31:07.174 --> 31:10.610
Shit, shit, shit.

31:10.612 --> 31:13.279
If this goes all Evil
Dead, I'm gonna pop!

31:13.281 --> 31:17.417
The zombies are coming!

31:17.419 --> 31:18.451
[screaming]

31:18.453 --> 31:19.321
Oh, my God!

31:22.190 --> 31:23.423
Hit him in the head!
Dax!

31:23.425 --> 31:23.991
Somebody!

31:23.993 --> 31:25.193
Get him...

31:30.466 --> 31:32.199
A hit to the head
takes them down.

31:32.201 --> 31:33.369
Wouldn't that kill anything?

31:41.613 --> 31:42.946
This is a GoPro.

31:42.948 --> 31:44.614
Walsh... he's filming us.

31:44.616 --> 31:45.582
KRILL: Oh, oh!

31:45.584 --> 31:47.850
Jesus.

31:47.852 --> 31:48.918
Ah!

31:48.920 --> 31:50.452
These... these things
are electrodes.

31:50.454 --> 31:52.288
Those things resurrect the dead.

31:52.290 --> 31:53.289
He's controlling them.

31:53.291 --> 31:56.294
[suspenseful music]

32:01.734 --> 32:03.701
I think I know where
the signal's coming from.

32:03.703 --> 32:04.636
Let's move.

32:04.638 --> 32:07.540
[zombies growling]

32:12.946 --> 32:14.946
Faster, faster, move faster!

32:14.948 --> 32:16.649
Go, go, go!
Come on.

32:16.651 --> 32:17.650
VIDEO GAME: Great!

32:17.652 --> 32:20.620
Powered up!

32:20.622 --> 32:23.923
Zombie needs food fast!

32:23.925 --> 32:26.926
