ever afraid of was you!

01:24:11.787 --> 01:24:13.356
Stop right there, Dax.

01:24:13.358 --> 01:24:14.290
Right now.

01:24:14.292 --> 01:24:15.224
No.

01:24:15.226 --> 01:24:17.994
